data.description: Make a call to see this value-priced home in one of the hottest Denver neighborhoods, Chaffee Park!  This cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath home on a quiet interior street is just minutes to I-70 and I-25 for an easy commute.  Pre-Inspected, including a roof certification, for peace of mind. Newer Simonton windows, hot water heater, security system, updated bath plus the HVAC was replaced in 2020! A big fenced backyard with a 29-foot patio, partially covered by a pergola, offers a great place to relax and enjoy your favorite beverage or BBQ with friends and family. This home is perfect for someone looking to build sweat equity.  Located just north of Sunnyside and the Highlands, you are within 15 minutes of downtown amenities, plus Coors Field and Empower Stadium.  At this price, this home will not last. Act today!
